resources.string: I hereby accept the AEPS Terms and Conditions and voluntarily consent to ICICI Bank to obtain my Aadhaar Virtual id and fingerprint for authentication with UIDAI. I have been informed that my identity information will be used for authentication and Bank will share Aadhaar number and/or biometrics with CIDR/UIDAI, and CIDR/UIDAI will share with Bank, authentication data/information which shall be used for the informed purpose of AePS transaction. The above consent and purpose of collecting Information has been explained to me in my local language.
